#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/community_technical_meeting.md:0
msgid "# 技术例会"
msgstr "# Technical Regular Meeting"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/community_technical_meeting.md:2
msgid "Triton-Ascend 定期召开社区技术会议，作为项目治理的核心决策机制。技术方向、重大提案评审和版本发布等重大事项在技术会议中讨论和决定，由全体 `Maintainer` 投票。会议对所有社区成员开放，任何人均可参与讨论，但决策和投票仅由 `Maintainer` 进行。"
msgstr "Triton-Ascend holds regular community technical meetings as the core decision-making mechanism for project governance. Major matters such as technical direction, major proposal reviews, and version releases are discussed and decided in the technical meetings, with voting conducted by all `Maintainer`s. The meetings are open to all community members, and anyone can participate in the discussions, but decisions and voting are carried out only by `Maintainer`s."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/community_technical_meeting.md:4
msgid "## 会议内容"
msgstr "## Meeting Content"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/community_technical_meeting.md:6
msgid ""
"- 技术方向讨论与决策\n"
"- 重大提案（RFC）评审与投票\n"
"- 版本发布规划与时间线\n"
"- 社区 Issue 和 PR 优先级排序\n"
"- 贡献者提名与移除讨论\n"
msgstr ""
"- Technical direction discussion and decision-making\n"
"- Major proposal (RFC) review and voting\n"
"- Version release planning and timeline\n"
"- Community Issue and PR priority sorting\n"
"- Contributor nomination and removal discussion\n"

