#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/community_technical_meeting.md:12
msgid "## 投票规则"
msgstr "## Voting Rules"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/community_technical_meeting.md:14
msgid ""
"- 未出席会议的 `Maintainer` 须在会议后 3 个工作日内提交投票；逾期未投票视为弃权\n"
"- 投票通过条件为参与投票的 `Maintainer` 超过半数同意（弃权不计入投票总数）\n"
"- 投票结果记录于会议纪要中\n"
msgstr ""
"- `Maintainer` who did not attend the meeting must submit their vote within 3 working days after the meeting; failure to vote within this period will be considered abstention.\n"
"- The condition for a vote to pass is that more than half of the participating `Maintainer` agree (abstentions are not counted in the total votes).\n"
"- The voting results are recorded in the meeting minutes.\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/community_technical_meeting.md:16
msgid "## 决策流程"
msgstr "## Decision Process"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/community_technical_meeting.md:18
msgid "### 常规决策"
msgstr "### Routine Decisions"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/community_technical_meeting.md:20
msgid "日常开发中的常规决策（如 `Bug` 修复、小功能改进）由相关模块的 `Maintainer` 在 `Issue` 或 `PR` 中审阅决定，无需召开会议。"
msgstr "Routine decisions in daily development (such as `Bug` fixes, small feature improvements) are reviewed and decided by the `Maintainer` of the relevant module in the `Issue` or `PR`, without the need for a meeting."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/community_technical_meeting.md:22
msgid "### 重大决策"
msgstr "### Major Decisions"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/community_technical_meeting.md:24
msgid "以下事项视为重大决策，需由 `Maintainer` 在社区技术会议中集体讨论："
msgstr "The following matters are considered major decisions and require collective discussion by `Maintainer` in the community technical meeting:"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/community_technical_meeting.md:26
msgid ""
"- 重大架构变更\n"
"- 破坏性 `API` 变更\n"
"- 新增核心功能或移除现有功能\n"
"- 第三方依赖的重大升级\n"
"- 版本发布规划\n"
msgstr ""
"- Major architectural changes\n"
"- Breaking `API` changes\n"
"- Addition of core features or removal of existing features\n"
"- Major upgrades of third-party dependencies\n"
"- Version release planning\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/community_technical_meeting.md:28
msgid "重大决策流程："
msgstr "Major Decision-Making Process:"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/community_technical_meeting.md:30
msgid ""
"1. 提交 `RFC`（征求意见稿），描述变更内容、影响范围和实施方案\n"
"2. 在技术会议中讨论\n"
"3. `Maintainer` 共同决策\n"
msgstr ""
"1. Submit an `RFC` (Request for Comments) describing the changes, scope of impact, and implementation plan\n"
"2. Discuss in the technical meeting\n"
"3. `Maintainer` makes a joint decision\n"

